trans-unit.source: Defines an encoder that is used to encode [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_tiff](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-tiff-md.md)] format images.
trans-unit.target: Definerer en koder som brukes til å kryptere [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_tiff](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-tiff-md.md)] formatere bilder.

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_tiff](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-tiff-md.md)] bitmap format supports frame level thumbnails, multiple frames, and frame level metadata.
trans-unit.target: Den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_tiff](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-tiff-md.md)] punktgrafikkformatet støtter ramme nivå miniatyrbilder, flere bilder og rammen nivå metadata.

trans-unit.source: It does not support global preview, global thumbnails, or global metadata.
trans-unit.target: Ikke støtter den globale forhåndsvisning, globale miniatyrbilder eller globale metadata.

trans-unit.source: Encoding does not work in partial trust.
trans-unit.target: Koding fungerer ikke med delvis klarering.

trans-unit.source: See [WPF Partial Trust Security](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) for information on partial trust.
trans-unit.target: Se [WPF delvis klarering sikkerhet](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) for informasjon om delvis klarering.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffBitmapEncoder"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffBitmapEncoder"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates the type of compression that is used by this [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_tiff](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-tiff-md.md)] image.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir kompresjonstype som brukes av dette [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_tiff](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-tiff-md.md)] bildet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffCompressOption>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffCompressOption>, and <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffCompressOption> values require that the <xref:System.Windows.Media.PixelFormat> value be set to <xref:System.Windows.Media.PixelFormats.BlackWhite%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffCompressOption>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffCompressOption>, og <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffCompressOption>verdier krever som <xref:System.Windows.Media.PixelFormat>verdien settes til <xref:System.Windows.Media.PixelFormats.BlackWhite%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Media.PixelFormats.BlackWhite%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Media.PixelFormat> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffCompressOption> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffCompressOption> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffCompressOption>
